# Torn Stat Tracker v2

This zip is set up as a Streamlit app.

## Local run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run streamlit_app.py
```

## Render
Use the included `render.yaml` or the start command below:
```bash
streamlit run streamlit_app.py --server.port=$PORT --server.address=0.0.0.0
```

## Notes
This is a Python app and needs a host that can run Python processes.
